body:
There's a [graph guide](https://www.tensorflow.org/guide/graphs) ([in github](https://github.com/tensorflow/docs/blob/master/site/en/guide/graphs.md)) if there are details you'd like to add.

Given the [emphasis on eager execution for TF 2.0](https://groups.google.com/a/tensorflow.org/forum/#!topic/announce/qXfsxr2sF-0), I don't think we'll building out this section much more.
